  "title": "Customer Service Officer/ Sales Support #81952",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Logistics</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Customer Service Officer/ Sales Support</strong></li><li>Working Location: Loyang</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days, Mon - Fri (9 AM – 6 PM) Sat (9 AM – 1 PM) (alternate Saturday upon confirmation)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle rate enquiries from customers and agents with timely, accurate quotes and options.</li><li>Liaise with carriers/co-loaders to secure competitive rates, handle RFQs, and support business targets.</li><li>Coordinate with the operations team to ensure smooth shipment execution.</li><li>Monitor market trends and support pricing proposals/strategies for clients.</li><li>Support key accounts through regular communication, pricing follow-ups, and report preparation.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81952 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
